he public stockholders were allegedly not fully informed of all material in=
formation about MultiPlan, they exchanged their right to $10.04 per share=
=E2=80=94held in a trust for their benefit=E2=80=94for an interest in Publi=
c MultiPlan.</p></blockquote><p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">And here is how V=
ice Chancellor Will describes the conflict:</p><blockquote><p style=3D"marg=
