hares would be locked up for 18 months, meaning that he=E2=80=99d lose mone=
y if the deal traded poorly. You can (and Klein=E2=80=99s lawyers did) poin=
t to this stuff and say that his incentives were aligned with the sharehold=
ers=E2=80=99, and that he=E2=80=99d do much better if the deal went well th=
an if it went poorly. The judge didn=E2=80=99t buy it:</p><blockquote><p st=
yle=3D"margin: 16px 0;">The defendants assert that the founder shares=E2=80=
